      "content": "Don't really need to dwell on the \"loss\" aspect, let's keep it positive. Just phrase it as an \"evolution towards efficiency.\" We want them to feel like the speed is a feature, not a downgrade. Try to draft the first few paragraphs for me now so I can show management.",
